{"tid":818805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風山竹】惡劣天氣或致停電　中電：密切監察並盡量維持可靠供電","createTime":"2018-09-14T10:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T11:51:10.000Z","uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2ff54d7697b222b58ecc17aab159f4c09cecbf","tid":818805,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"超強颱風「山竹」迫港，港府嚴陣以待。中電表示，惡劣天氣有機會引致電壓驟降、供電不穩甚或停電，對客戶可能構成不便，中電將密切監察風暴可能對供電系統造成的影響，並採取相關措施盡量維持可靠供電。 <br />\n<br />\n發言人又指，如任何市民發現戶外電線斷落或電線杆倒塌，或風暴期間遇上停電事故，可立刻致電中電24小時緊急服務熱線2728 8333，提醒電線或仍然帶電，切勿觸摸或試圖將其移離。 <br />\n<br />\n中電稱，如出現廣泛地區停電，將安排優先為需要電力儀器維持生命的客戶，及供公共服務的機構優先復電，如醫院、鐵路、機場、廣播機構及電訊機構等。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2161183/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%91%E6%83%A1%E5%8A%A3%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9A%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%A6%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2161183%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258A%25A3%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%259B%25BB%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%259B%25BB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%2588%2587%25E7%259B%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%25E4%25BE%259B%25E9%259B%25BB&d=Z%2FX2r%2BYHNENfykGPwY00Y8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=577a3135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2161183/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%91%E6%83%A1%E5%8A%A3%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9A%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%A6%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%BB</a><br />